reviews.text: Got tired from work and Mcdo is just everywhere so here i am having my fav burgers.. 1 for breakfast and 1 for lunch
Small one. Still an attraction to students from schools around.
It's the place I always loved to stay with when I'm starving when the time I am free...
The food taste good.

Visited in the morning of the 1st day of Chinese New Year, I guess the lady working at the McCafe might be temporary staff. Not complaint but just to record my experience. Very poor experience in terms of services and coffee quality. The staff looked angry and spoke with “strong” tone (thinking in the best positive mind could be that she was very serious and focusing on the work), so never mind. I was handicapped with broken right arm, so I was not able to hold the board with a tall glass of coffee and a dish of bread on it using my left hand only. She saw that but hadn’t offered any help. So, I took the glass of coffee and the dish of bread myself separately. For the coffee quality (I ordered latte), in terms of look, not appealing to me. In terms of taste, very very light taste, no structure and details at all, perhaps just not my preferred type of coffee. 

0 star on services & 0 star on latte

result.name: Kowloon City Plaza

reviews.text: Kowloon City Plaza is a typical shopping mall in a residental area of Hong Kong. It is a fancy-free very down to earth place which would not attract much attention to tourists who might look for international brand names. But tourists are not the target customers - locals are.This attraction is of little interest to a tourist . Each level of the plaza has shops of similar theme.For instance,one level is dedicated to telecommunications. Rather than having food in the plaza,venture out to one of the many eateries located on the streets nearby.
A great shopping mall for the locals.
A quiet shopping mall.

Lots of shops closed down, it's our only place to cool down in the hot summer. Need to bring in trendy hk cafe, Japanese restaurants, and Taiwanese restaurants into the mall. Would have been a dream came true to have indoor children playground, and I am not talking about the children zone that is currently at the basement.
Lots of shops with good deals, and the supermarket has a big sale each Tuesday so go there and see if you have been lucky!

reviews.text: 店多
從小在這裡成長😁
Good👍
有2酒楼及連鎖食肆如麥記、KFC、吉之島百货超市及顶楼兒童小型赛車埸、2層大型停車场，市民必需品商店齊備，惟沒賣名牌！美中不足欠影院帶旺！非假日人少但購物舒服，吉之岛每周中超市九折，假日購物滿$400有免泊2Hrs，而平日只需$200!
在這裡的Starbucks買了一個杯，非常快樂。
